            "name": "ANCA-Associated Vasculitis",
            "confidence": 0.5,
            "icd_code": "M31.30",
            "reasoning": "Hematuria, proteinuria, and renal dysfunction could represent renal involvement in ANCA-associated vasculitis. Pending ANCA results will help clarify. The episodic nature and lack of systemic symptoms make this less likely."
        },
