            "name": "Thin Basement Membrane Disease",
            "confidence": 0.4,
            "icd_code": "N02.2",
            "reasoning": "Given the patient's age, family history of kidney disease, and persistent hematuria, thin basement membrane disease is possible. However, the significant proteinuria, RBC casts, and declining renal function are atypical."
        },
        {
            "name": "Occupational Nephropathy",
            "confidence": 0.3,
            "icd_code": "N14.4",
